<section
  id="education"
  class="relative flex min-h-[50vh] w-full items-start m-auto mt-12 md:mt-40"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto md:px-4">
    <div class="w-full md:max-w-6xl m-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl mb-1 text-center"
      >
        Formación Académica
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground text-center mb-8 text-pretty">
        Creciendo profesionalmente a través del aprendizaje constante.
      </p>

      <div
        class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground group relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-background to-background p-1 shadow-xl border-input"
      >
        <div class="relative rounded-lg bg-card p-6">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-lg pointer-events-none"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:gap-8"
          >
            <div class="lg:w-1/3">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight">
                  Análisis y Desarrollo de Software
                </h3>
              </div><div
                class="mt-2 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"
              >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-graduation-cap h-4 w-4"
                    ><path
                      d="M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z"
                    ></path><path d="M22 10v6"></path><path
                      d="M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5"></path></svg
                  ><span>SENA: Servicio Nacional de Aprendizaje</span>
                </div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4"
                    ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
                      width="18"
                      height="18"
                      x="3"
                      y="4"
                      rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg
                  >
                  <span>Nov 2023 - Actualidad</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-2/3">
              <p
                class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground"
                style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
              >
                Actualmente finalizando la etapa lectiva del programa Tecnólogo
                en Análisis y Desarrollo de Software en el SENA, enfocado en el
                desarrollo de aplicaciones web con buenas prácticas y
                metodologías ágiles.
              </p><div
                class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2"
                style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
              >
                <span
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20"
                  >Análisis y diseño de software</span
                ><span
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20"
                  >Programación web</span
                ><span
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20"
                  >Bases de datos</span
                ><span
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20"
                  >Control de versiones</span
                >
              </div><ul
                class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2"
                style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
              >
                <li
                  class="flex items-start gap-2"
                  style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-badge-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-primary"
                    ><path
                      d="M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z"
                    ></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg
                  ><span class="text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground"
                    >Mantener un alto rendimiento académico</span
                  >
                </li><li
                  class="flex items-start gap-2"
                  style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-badge-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-primary"
                    ><path
                      d="M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z"
                    ></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg
                  ><span class="text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground"
                    >Comprometido con el aprendizaje continuo</span
                  >
                </li><li
                  class="flex items-start gap-2"
                  style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-badge-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-primary"
                    ><path
                      d="M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z"
                    ></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg
                  ><span class="text-sm leading-tight text-muted-foreground"
                    >Enfocado en la calidad del código y la mejora constante</span
                  >
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
